<br>
The old excuse &quot;I wasn't sure what it was worth&quot; holds no water whatsoever, seeing as how there are several web pages out there with continuously updated pricings, not to mention plenty of people right there in EC who will be more than happy to answer your &quot;price check!&quot;<br>
<br>
It's all well and fine that there are people out there who get their jollies buying and selling, I just hate the total ripoff attitude most people seem to have in the process.  I don't mind people making a profit, but I seriously mind people trying to take advantage of me.<br>
<br>
Let this serve as a warning to the next person who replies to me with &quot;make an offer&quot; on a platinum based trade.  You can cram it up your rectum for that and all future business.  I won't hesitate to tell everyone I know you are a waste of time to deal with as well.<br>
<br>
Sweet baby jesus I wish this was a pk server sometimes.<br>
<br>
