</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uvirrallootaholic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Virral Lootaholic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 356<br> <font color=#E9D756>(6/28/01 6:16:58 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Greedy Fucks</span><hr size=1> Works both ways Brodie, Im guessing if they did set a price and it was too low, your not going to say &quot;whoah dude, its worth five times that&quot;<br>
<br>
